Class Vertex_List<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • graph.Vertex<T>
      • graph.Vertex_List<T>

  • public class Vertex_List<T>
extends Vertex<T>
    Class name: Vertex_List General Description: This class extends the base class Vertex and represents a vertex in an adjacency list in a graph. It has additional parent and adjacent fields that are used in certain graph search and traversal algorithms.
